  <name>Shortcut</name>
  <summary>Make desktop files</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Shortcut is a tool that allows users to quickly pin executable files to their app launcher for
      quick
      access.

      It guides users throught the process by providing file picker dialogs with relevant filters,
      input validation, and name and icon previews.
    </p>
  </description>
